#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:52
#: ebd5f7607e734471a5619b031be5b080
msgid "Weak form and stabilization"
msgstr "弱形式与稳定化"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:54
#: 70247aa9d1de492e8007211efd4d5ce6
msgid ""
"The standard mixed weak form treats velocity and pressure together. Because "
"the scripts use **equal-order** P1-P1 elements for both, the discrete LBB "
"condition is violated and the naive Galerkin formulation has spurious "
"pressure modes. The fix is **SUPG/PSPG stabilization**: add a residual-based"
" perturbation to both the momentum and the continuity equations, scaled by a"
" mesh-size-dependent parameter :math:`\\tau`."
msgstr ""
"标准的混合弱形式将速度与压力一并处理。由于这些脚本对两者都采用\\ **等阶** P1-P1 单元，离散 LBB "
"条件被违反，朴素的伽辽金格式会出现伪压力模态。解决办法是 **SUPG/PSPG 稳定化**\\ "
"：向动量方程和连续性方程都加入一个基于残差的扰动项，并以依赖网格尺寸的参数 :math:`\\tau` 进行缩放。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:61
#: 2fe71123f8654297ad2288c412d12086
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Denote by :math:`\\mathbf{w} = \\mathbf{w}^{n}` the  velocity at the "
"previous Picard iterate. The SUPG/PSPG-stabilized weak form seeks "
":math:`\\mathbf{u} \\in (H^1_0(\\Omega))^d + \\mathbf{u}_b` and :math:`p "
"\\in L^2(\\Omega)/\\mathbb{R}` such that for all :math:`\\mathbf{v} \\in "
"(H^1_0(\\Omega))^d, q \\in L^2(\\Omega)/\\mathbb{R}`,"
msgstr ""
"记 :math:`\\mathbf{w} = \\mathbf{w}^{n}` 为上一个 Picard 迭代步的速度。SUPG/PSPG "
"稳定化弱形式寻求 :math:`\\mathbf{u} \\in (H^1_0(\\Omega))^d + \\mathbf{u}_b` 和 "
":math:`p \\in L^2(\\Omega)/\\mathbb{R}`\\ ，使得对所有 :math:`\\mathbf{v} \\in "
"(H^1_0(\\Omega))^d, q \\in L^2(\\Omega)/\\mathbb{R}`\\ ，"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:65
#: c1e89f879f4f491ba8511d9101e94dc0
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\int_\\Omega \\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}\\cdot\\mathbf{v}\\,\\mathrm{d}x\n"
"+ \\int_\\Omega \\mu\\,\\nabla\\mathbf{u} : \\nabla\\mathbf{v}\\,\\mathrm{d}x\n"
"- \\int_\\Omega p\\,(\\nabla\\cdot\\mathbf{v})\\,\\mathrm{d}x \\;+\n"
"\\int_\\Omega q\\,(\\nabla\\cdot\\mathbf{u})\\,\\mathrm{d}x \\;=\\; 0 ."
msgstr ""
"\\int_\\Omega \\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}\\cdot\\mathbf{v}\\,\\mathrm{d}x\n"
"+ \\int_\\Omega \\mu\\,\\nabla\\mathbf{u} : \\nabla\\mathbf{v}\\,\\mathrm{d}x\n"
"- \\int_\\Omega p\\,(\\nabla\\cdot\\mathbf{v})\\,\\mathrm{d}x \\;+\n"
"\\int_\\Omega q\\,(\\nabla\\cdot\\mathbf{u})\\,\\mathrm{d}x \\;=\\; 0 ."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:72
#: 3b8356a1c6714e798a4850d06870942a
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Here, :math:`\\mathbf{u}_b` incorporates the non-homogeneous velocity "
"boundary conditions; :math:`L^2(\\Omega)/\\mathbb{R}` is the space modulo "
"constants (since pressure is only determined up to an additive constant)."
msgstr ""
"这里 :math:`\\mathbf{u}_b` 计入了非齐次的速度边界条件；\\ :math:`L^2(\\Omega)/\\mathbb{R}` "
"是模去常数后的空间（因为压力只能确定到一个相加常数）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:74
#: da678a3f8bc94ceca6f40008b54df9f4
msgid ""
"For equal-order P1-P1 this Galerkin form is unstable, so we append element-"
"wise **SUPG/PSPG** terms built from the strong momentum residual"
msgstr "对于等阶 P1-P1，这一伽辽金形式是不稳定的，因此我们逐单元附加由强动量残差构造的 **SUPG/PSPG** 项"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:76
#: 2d2241cfacbf41f1ab6b495dd56311ed
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\mathbf{R}(\\mathbf{u}, p) \\;=\\;\n"
"\\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u} + \\nabla p - \\mu\\,\\Delta\\mathbf{u}."
msgstr ""
"\\mathbf{R}(\\mathbf{u}, p) \\;=\\;\n"
"\\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u} + \\nabla p - \\mu\\,\\Delta\\mathbf{u}."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:81
#: 7745946759e0445f85473ebf7a2ea905
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Note that the viscous term :math:`\\mu\\,\\Delta\\mathbf{u}` vanishes on P1 "
"elements. The stabilized discretization uses P1-P1 elements for "
":math:`\\mathbf{u}` and :math:`p`, and adds"
msgstr ""
"注意黏性项 :math:`\\mu\\,\\Delta\\mathbf{u}` 在 P1 单元上为零。该稳定化离散对 "
":math:`\\mathbf{u}` 和 :math:`p` 都使用 P1-P1 单元，并加入"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:83
#: a80aed8449dc457d9e934bcfd4127a46
msgid ""
"\\underbrace{\\sum_e \\int_{\\Omega_e}\n"
"    \\tau\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{v}\\cdot\\mathbf{R}\\,\\mathrm{d}x}_{\\text{SUPG}}\n"
"\\;+\\;\n"
"\\underbrace{\\sum_e \\int_{\\Omega_e}\n"
"    \\tau\\,\\nabla q\\cdot\\mathbf{R}\\,\\mathrm{d}x}_{\\text{PSPG}}"
msgstr ""
"\\underbrace{\\sum_e \\int_{\\Omega_e}\n"
"    \\tau\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{v}\\cdot\\mathbf{R}\\,\\mathrm{d}x}_{\\text{SUPG}}\n"
"\\;+\\;\n"
"\\underbrace{\\sum_e \\int_{\\Omega_e}\n"
"    \\tau\\,\\nabla q\\cdot\\mathbf{R}\\,\\mathrm{d}x}_{\\text{PSPG}}"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:91
#: 3a594e41f2d54494b08d1ebf7f41da29
msgid ""
"to the aforementioned weak form, with :math:`\\tau` being a stabilization "
"parameter."
msgstr "到上述弱形式中，其中 :math:`\\tau` 为稳定化参数。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:93
#: cd089d0e4e734327a7520c249b6891b6
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The implementation is a custom :class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` defined"
" locally in the example. Its ``forward`` returns the :math:`(d{+}1) \\times "
"(d{+}1)` block coupling one test node to one trial node — :math:`d` velocity"
" components plus pressure — which the assembler stamps into a block-COO "
"sparse matrix exactly as the built-in vector-valued assemblers do. The block"
" is built from four named sub-blocks rather than entry-by-entry, so each "
"physical term is visible:"
msgstr ""
"其实现是一个在算例中本地定义的自定义 :class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler`\\ 。它的 ``forward`` "
"返回耦合一个测试节点与一个试探节点的 :math:`(d{+}1) \\times (d{+}1)` 块——即 :math:`d` "
"个速度分量加上压力——装配器会像内置的向量值装配器那样，将该块印入一个块状 COO "
"稀疏矩阵。这个块是由四个具名子块而非逐项构造的，因此每个物理项都清晰可见："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:102
#: 906ddada6db04bf8ac3d24445a0b9036
msgid "examples/fluid/cavity/cavity.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/fluid/cavity/cavity.py（核心部分）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:128
#: 46c5cfb158604f659d7f5d065ce71ce2
msgid ""
"The four named sub-blocks map one-to-one onto the terms of the stabilized "
"weak form above:"
msgstr "这四个具名子块与上面稳定化弱形式中的各项一一对应："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:131
#: 618e7780cb394fe4b7267f7b78dae7f6
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``A_uu`` — convection "
":math:`\\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}\\cdot\\mathbf{v}`, "
"diffusion :math:`\\mu\\,\\nabla\\mathbf{u}:\\nabla\\mathbf{v}`, and the SUPG"
" convection term "
":math:`\\tau\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla\\mathbf{v})\\,\\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}`"
" (diagonal in the components, hence ``* eye``);"
msgstr ""
"``A_uu``——对流项 "
":math:`\\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}\\cdot\\mathbf{v}`\\ "
"、扩散项 :math:`\\mu\\,\\nabla\\mathbf{u}:\\nabla\\mathbf{v}`\\ ，以及 SUPG 对流项 "
":math:`\\tau\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla\\mathbf{v})\\,\\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}`\\"
" （在各分量上是对角的，故乘以 ``* eye``\\ ）；"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:135
#: ec0eefbbf2a74cbfb313a03a97aabe40
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``B_up`` — pressure gradient :math:`-p\\,\\nabla\\cdot\\mathbf{v}` and its "
"SUPG counterpart "
":math:`\\tau\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla\\mathbf{v})\\cdot\\nabla p`;"
msgstr ""
"``B_up``——压力梯度项 :math:`-p\\,\\nabla\\cdot\\mathbf{v}` 及其 SUPG 对应项 "
":math:`\\tau\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla\\mathbf{v})\\cdot\\nabla p`\\ ；"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:137
#: 90c358b97ee94db0812d28efc007a8df
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``B_pu`` — divergence :math:`q\\,\\nabla\\cdot\\mathbf{u}` and the PSPG "
"convection term :math:`\\tau\\,\\nabla "
"q\\cdot\\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}`;"
msgstr ""
"``B_pu``——散度项 :math:`q\\,\\nabla\\cdot\\mathbf{u}` 及 PSPG 对流项 "
":math:`\\tau\\,\\nabla "
"q\\cdot\\rho\\,(\\mathbf{w}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}`\\ ；"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:139
#: 61beb7ec485f41cd8ba27598b27f8fa6
msgid "``C_pp`` — the PSPG pressure-Laplacian :math:`\\tau\\,\\nabla p\\cdot\\nabla q`."
msgstr "``C_pp``——PSPG 压力拉普拉斯项 :math:`\\tau\\,\\nabla p\\cdot\\nabla q`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:141
#: 06e1f1e38c9948518548f697d8ad9d3b
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Because ``dim`` is read from ``gradu.shape[0]``, the same ``forward`` "
"produces a :math:`3{\\times}3` block in 2D and a :math:`4{\\times}4` block "
"in 3D with no changes."
msgstr ""
"由于 ``dim`` 是从 ``gradu.shape[0]`` 读取的，同一个 ``forward`` 在 2D 中产生 "
":math:`3{\\times}3` 块、在 3D 中产生 :math:`4{\\times}4` 块，无需任何改动。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:147
#: 3bc4ffe1a6c14a359c9dc70c2d28768a
msgid "Picard iteration"
msgstr "Picard 迭代"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:149
#: 86c25ada4b7d4529b1cb98163850a41c
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The convection term :math:`(\\mathbf{u}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}` is "
"linearized by passing the previous-iterate velocity :math:`\\mathbf{w}^{n}` "
"as ``w_prev`` to the assembler:"
msgstr ""
"对流项 :math:`(\\mathbf{u}\\cdot\\nabla)\\mathbf{u}` 通过将上一迭代步的速度 "
":math:`\\mathbf{w}^{n}` 作为 ``w_prev`` 传给装配器来线性化："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:153
#: bc2c7a08e22748a1b6d1eccb499b6e15
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\rho\\, (\\mathbf{w}^{n} \\cdot \\nabla)\\mathbf{u}^{n+1}\n"
"\\;=\\; -\\nabla p^{n+1} + \\mu\\, \\Delta \\mathbf{u}^{n+1}."
msgstr ""
"\\rho\\, (\\mathbf{w}^{n} \\cdot \\nabla)\\mathbf{u}^{n+1}\n"
"\\;=\\; -\\nabla p^{n+1} + \\mu\\, \\Delta \\mathbf{u}^{n+1}."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:158
#: 4780c86931fa461fafe7c3e3b55c8c5e
msgid ""
"This converges geometrically for moderate Reynolds numbers; the script "
"iterates until ``||u_new - u_full|| / ||u_new|| < 1e-4``, typically ~8 "
"iterations at Re=100."
msgstr ""
"对于中等雷诺数，该过程以几何速率收敛；脚本迭代直到 ``||u_new - u_full|| / ||u_new|| < 1e-4``\\ ，在 "
"Re=100 时通常约需 8 次迭代。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:179
#: 1ba1524481114f36b314104fc7c419f6
msgid "A few details that matter:"
msgstr "几个需要注意的细节："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:181
#: 70e18321f3f74ed88ad9d6a7c2c2dd20
msgid ""
"**DOF layout.** The unknowns are interleaved node-major: ``[u_0, v_0, p_0, "
"u_1, v_1, p_1, …]`` in 2D (``[u, v, w, p]`` per node in 3D). The script's "
"small ``component_dofs(n_points, n_dof, comp)`` helper turns \"component "
"``comp`` at every node\" into the flat global indices the "
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` mask expects."
msgstr ""
"**自由度排布。**\\ 未知量以节点为主序交错排列：2D 中为 ``[u_0, v_0, p_0, u_1, v_1, p_1, …]``\\ （3D"
" 中每个节点为 ``[u, v, w, p]``\\ ）。脚本中小巧的 ``component_dofs(n_points, n_dof, "
"comp)`` 辅助函数将“每个节点上的分量 ``comp``”转换为 :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` "
"掩码所需的扁平全局索引。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:186
#: de5d951b9d614c298a5ece9a8f487e7b
msgid ""
"**Pressure pin.** ``bc_mask[n_dof - 1] = True`` clamps pressure to zero at "
"node 0 — required because pressure is only determined up to an additive "
"constant in incompressible flow."
msgstr ""
"**压力钉定。**\\ ``bc_mask[n_dof - 1] = True`` 将节点 0 "
"处的压力钉定为零——这是必要的，因为不可压缩流动中压力只能确定到一个相加常数。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:189
#: 5f034c8edcae4c1094a92165bf48a2cd
msgid ""
"``w_prev`` is passed by name in ``point_data`` and arrives in ``forward`` as"
" the matching keyword argument; see :doc:`../../user_guide/forms` for the "
"dispatch contract."
msgstr ""
"``w_prev`` 通过 ``point_data`` 按名称传入，并作为同名关键字参数到达 ``forward``\\ ；分发约定参见 "
":doc:`../../user_guide/forms`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:193
#: ce5f9e8f47f04a41928794fc173ad056
msgid "Lid-driven cavity speed magnitude and pressure at Re=100"
msgstr "Re=100 时顶盖驱动方腔的速度大小与压力"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cavity.rst:197
#: 0970c80c6eb74e32b929d0293617d1f4
msgid ""
"Output of ``cavity.py`` at Re = 100. Left: speed magnitude :math:`\\|u\\|` —"
" the moving lid drags fluid into the upper right, sweeping it down the right"
" wall and forming the primary vortex. Right: pressure field, with the "
"characteristic high-pressure spot in the upper-right corner where the lid "
"stagnates against the wall."
msgstr ""
"``cavity.py`` 在 Re = 100 时的输出。左：速度大小 "
":math:`\\|u\\|`——运动顶盖将流体拖向右上方，再沿右壁向下扫掠，形成主涡。右：压力场，在顶盖与壁面相撞滞止的右上角出现特征性的高压区。"

